org.gnode.nix

Class DataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gnode.nix.DataType

  • public class DataType
extends Object

    DataType

    Constants for all valid data types.

    Those data types are used by DataArray and Property in order to indicate of what type the stored data of value is.

    See Also:
    DataArray, Property
